        <h2>Revenue Path</h2>
        <p>Parachute Computer is free and open source&mdash;that's the growth engine. Revenue comes from making it easier for people who don't want to self-host:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Hosted Parachute Computer</strong>&mdash;a managed service where you get your own Parachute Computer without running a server.</li>
            <li><strong>Standalone Daily app</strong>&mdash;a simpler journal-focused entry point for people who aren't ready for the full platform.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>February focuses on users. Revenue experimentation starts March once real usage patterns show which path has the most pull.</p>
